# Git Workflow

Defaults:
- Branch creation requires explicit instruction.
- Branch switching requires explicit instruction.
- Commits require explicit instruction.
- Push requires explicit instruction.
- One branch should map to one active spec by default.

Preferred base branch: `{{ workflow.base_branch }}`

Branch strategy: `{{ workflow.branch_strategy }}`

Before modifying files, report:

```bash
git status --short
git branch --show-current
git branch --all
git log --oneline -5
```
